snippet.title: Spellsworn Bot trailer
snippet.description:
Bots are now available in Spellsworn, thanks to the efforts of this determined acolyte! And now, with Bots, skins, tradingcards, features and more, Spellsworn has now entered Alpha stage!

Find out more about Spellsworn here - http://store.steampowered.com/app/360620/

Created by Frogsong Studios

Twitter - https://twitter.com/FrogsongStudios

Facebook - https://www.facebook.com/FrogsongStudios/


Music by Maciek Dobrowolski - https://twitter.com/maciekdobro
